REQUIREMENTS

PyCosmic is based purely on Python.
The following Python packages are required to be installed on the system:

Python 2.5 or later (recommended is at least Python 2.6 for parallel processing)
pyfits 2.2.2 (or later) or astropy any version
numpy 1.3.0 or later
scipy 0.7.1 or later


Please note that PyCosmic was successfully tested with the package versions listed  above, 
but earlier versions of individual packages might work with PyCosmic and later version may not be downward compatible. 

